<section id="output" class="container-full section-space border-t border-border">
  <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.75fr)_minmax(0,1.25fr)] lg:gap-16">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <p class="label-accent">The output</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-section-title text-balance">Decisions, not a decorative strategy deck.</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.7] text-muted md:text-base">
        Every initiative ends with a decision record that connects the evidence reviewed to a clear
        recommendation and a named next action.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-5 border-l-2 border-accent pl-5 text-[0.9375rem] font-medium leading-[1.7] text-ink md:text-base">
        Time saved is not presented as financial value unless that capacity can be redeployed, cost
        can be removed or revenue-producing work can increase.
      </p>
    </div>

    <article class="border border-ink/20 bg-white">
      <header class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-ink/15 px-5 py-4 md:px-7">
        <h3 class="text-base">Decision record</h3>
        <span class="text-sm text-muted">Included for each initiative</span>
      </header>

      <dl class="divide-y divide-border">
        <div class="grid gap-2 px-5 py-5 md:grid-cols-[150px_1fr] md:px-7">
          <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Initiative</dt>
          <dd class="text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.6] text-muted">
            Current purpose, cost, owner and renewal point.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-2 px-5 py-5 md:grid-cols-[150px_1fr] md:px-7">
          <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Evidence</dt>
          <dd class="text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.6] text-muted">
            Usage data, workflow observation, stakeholder accounts and financial assumptions.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-2 px-5 py-5 md:grid-cols-[150px_1fr] md:px-7">
          <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Decision</dt>
          <dd class="text-[0.9375rem] font-semibold leading-[1.6] text-accent">
            Stop, repair, consolidate or expand.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-2 px-5 py-5 md:grid-cols-[150px_1fr] md:px-7">
          <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Next 90 days</dt>
          <dd class="text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.6] text-muted">
            Named owner, baseline measure, first action and decision checkpoint.
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
